	•	Mocks the FinancialInstitutionService to test only the controller layer.
	•	Uses MockMvc to simulate REST API calls.
	•	Validates API responses (JSON format, status codes, and expected values).
	•	Handles different scenarios (successful response, empty results, exceptions).

