Bad Request	IllegalArgumentException	400 Bad Request	"Invalid request parameters"
Database Failure	RuntimeException	500 Internal Server Error	"Database connection failed"
Generic Exception	RuntimeException	500 Internal Server Error	"Unexpected error occurred"
Request ID Included	RuntimeException	500 Internal Server Error	"Internal server error"

